column2: "You're ARKS too right? I'll give you a word of advice."
"This place is dangerous. You should leave if you don't have any reason to be here."
"Not like there's anything in this area in particular, just that Naberius is dangerous in general."
"Well, I warned you, so if you still want to poke around, that's your business."
"It's not like I'm involved or anything."
